cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

The paper discusses the use of deep learning methods for image colorization, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) and Inception-ResNet-v2 model also suggests that the paper may belong to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The mention of a user study and applications on historical photographs suggests that the paper may also belong to multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories.
